1. *Požar* je izbio u sredu uveče. (A fire broke out on Wednesday evening.)
2. *Požar* je izazvao veliku štetu. (The fire caused a lot of damage.)
3. *Požar* je bio kontrolisan posle sat vremena. (The fire was under control after an hour.)
4. *Požarom* su izgorela tri zgrada. (Three buildings burned down in the fire.)
5. Vatrogasci su uspeli da uguše *požar*. (The firefighters managed to put out the fire.)
6. Policija još istražuje uzroke *požara*. (The police are still investigating the cause of the fire.)